Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:14.69,OP,,0,0,0,,真っ赤な線を描いたちっぽけな心の話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:21.03,OP,,0,0,0,,僕らの未来はどこに向かって光るの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:28.00,OP,,0,0,0,,続きの線を描いた　色づいてしまう度にまぶしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.46,OP,,0,0,0,,そんな心のリズムを繋ぎだす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.97,OP,,0,0,0,,かなしいかなしいかなしいかなしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:47.68,OP,,0,0,0,,うれしいうれしいうれしいうれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:54.47,OP,,0,0,0,,２つの感情に揺さぶられては
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:01:02.02,OP,,0,0,0,,まだ見ぬ指先を照らし出してくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:09.20,OP,,0,0,0,,このまま嘘でもいいから夢泳がせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:14.90,OP,,0,0,0,,かなしいかなしい今を探してく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:22.51,OP,,0,0,0,,僕らは見えない未来を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:28.38,OP,,0,0,0,,だから悲しい悲しい今を探しては光った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:29.54,OP,,0,0,0,,引つかた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:14.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}画下等待的长线 这是心中小小的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:21.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们的未来 到底会走向何方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:28.00,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}画下连续的长线 接下来的旅途必定也耀眼夺目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.46,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}就这样 连接上心的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:40.97,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}悲伤 悲伤 悲伤和悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:47.68,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}快乐 快乐 快乐和快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:54.47,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}把两份感伤的心叠放在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:01:02.02,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}看不清的未来里谁才是该出场的配角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.32,0:01:09.20,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}就这样下去 即使是谎言也让我把这美梦做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:14.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}悲伤地 悲伤地 现在就去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:22.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们相信着看不见的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:28.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}悲伤地 悲伤地 去寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:29.54,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}现在就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:35.00,Staff,,0,0,0,,字幕制作:雪飘工作室 翻译: 南方原润 手抄: NoobNeo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明约好九点在这里见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先开车过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在车站和莉莉奈他们会和后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再一起坐电车过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.04,0:01:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 是在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我非要拉他来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来了就说声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先说好 把我叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后难堪的是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 我把美咲带来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.01,0:02:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂同学怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.30,0:02:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那时的变态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 这个人怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过要带朋友来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.16,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,即使如此也不能叫这种奇怪的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.64,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,仁坂不是奇怪的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:25.10,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,什么才叫变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:28.56,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,除了变态以外这个人还能是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.10,0:02:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.28,0:02:23.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对莉莉干什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说别人的朋友变态啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说变态是变态有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我遭受了多大的屈辱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得 场面好尴尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能再委婉点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过政府通知来了真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我才能和美咲成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们平常都是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 刚才我和莉莉奈争吵的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和高崎同学说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:24.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂果然对高崎同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 我们要去整理小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和朋友们先准备一下午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 一来就让你帮忙真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们打算做咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 仁坂看起来很擅长做菜的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是那种会从1米高的地方倒橄榄油的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小根 我不会切肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.06,0:04:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你刚刚是打算切肉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着种要切骨的气势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你都没有用到右手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.77,0:04:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家庭课上没教过你左手要用猫爪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫爪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 难道你其实是个料理笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 仁坂你去洗菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洗菜你应该会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当我是傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 小根
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用多少洗洁精啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 最近的帅哥还会做菜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 他真的什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈 高崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲 快过来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还挺深的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.69,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,快看 那里有鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:29.15,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:31.03,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,是那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:32.42,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.41,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.24,TopHorizontalCenter,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 这种场面不该偷看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 即使不能看下装
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上方的泳衣应该是可以看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 你在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边很舒服的 由佳吏也过来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 美咲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.03,0:05:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我只是过来叫她们吃饭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在那自言自语什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像扭伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来背你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是感染细菌就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我才不要人背呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要把双腿打开骑上去多难看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在意的是这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别摔到我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽力的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎同学 能拜托你把莉莉奈的东西带回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 你快把莉莉奈带回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然好不容易抱起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这比我想象中还要亲密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 要保持平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 女孩子的皮肤好棒啊 好柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还滑滑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:06:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是第一次摸到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 有一股好闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 可不能摔到她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋由佳吏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 你的脚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意力分散之后脚就不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你把我抱回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊 莉莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你 为什么要来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.41,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是受虐狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根岛同学和莉莉我都很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉听说我要来的时候很高兴 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 莉莉奈那家伙怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.17,0:08:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂同学才是受虐狂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则也不会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么 别这么轻易就承认了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎同学和仁坂在一起 也会有那种表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不疼了那应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈的父亲是兽医
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好帅啊 像是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兽医本来就是专业的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏将来想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没有决定想去哪所大学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢古坟 所以打算朝这个方向努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 不过你为什么会喜欢古坟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古坟出现的时候 日本还没有文字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就算进入了保存近两千年的巨型古坟里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法知道当时的详情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也无法知道这里的主人生前是怎样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被葬在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠想象得出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这不是一件很厉害的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢一边想象着这个主人的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边踏入古坟的那个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还挺热衷研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么喜欢古坟的话就好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道 应该在开女子会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱话题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎现在一定很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 仁坂大概早就知道我喜欢高崎同学了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为了照顾我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说仁坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你靠的太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 你是不是有什么事瞒着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.18,0:10:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事瞒着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小根 我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 你出来下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美咲 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.47,0:11:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 我们来玩试胆大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就两人组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕着登山路线走圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过请别进入我的一米范围以内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你叫我变态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为那时的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是处女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此以外还有别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一句话就记到现在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是替小根的未来担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏是不会做出让对方讨厌的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 他又笨又靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底也没有什么优点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他很率直很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能真心接受我的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:54.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人都会因为自尊或感情原因做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许他就是没有自尊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我觉得这是他的优点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你意外地...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说着话就到了折返地点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.96,0:12:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不知道他们那边怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是由佳吏和美咲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种夜下的森林里两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会怎么样呢 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你一整天都这样让他们俩呆在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 因为他们俩不是两情相悦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道自己在干什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈真是强硬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次试胆大会也是莉莉奈提出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但是我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.29,0:12:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈给你添麻烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你已经完全把她当成家人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:12:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话 我们牵着手走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天这么黑了 很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 如果白天扭伤脚的人是我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会这样帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会 我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我没有莉莉那么纤细呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 刚刚是不是有什么飞过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 那棵树附近有什么在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎同学 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能这样待一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又没有做什么违法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我该换个说法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在中间做媒撮合小根和高崎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时 你又该站在什么立场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我会在他们二人...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就呆在他们二人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之类的说法 真是太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果小根选择了高崎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是说他选择放弃与你之间的政府通知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时你对他而言是个外人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且算是个朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友这种东西 要是贪心不足就会立刻结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那时你和小根 以及嫁给了小根的高崎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能继续做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然能了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能会嫁给不认识的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那或许会是个比小根更笨更靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至比我还变态的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知如此你还要撮合他们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我却无法赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提 如果如你所想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小根拒绝了政府通知的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当然无所谓 小根却会陷入麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.47,0:15:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府通知只是帮人缔结姻缘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使违反了应该也不会受到惩罚才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.85,0:15:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面上是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 如果真的拒绝了那就是另外一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以小根举例
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在傍晚时说的那个梦想会很难实现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而小根的目标 附近的县立大学也会变得很难考
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有出色的成绩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定会因为有拒绝过政府通知这样的案底而被刷下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 你现在的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只会给小根带来不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是很喜欢美咲和由佳吏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望他们俩能开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种想法也只存在于童话世界而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是不是有什么发光的东西飞过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在飞呢 是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由佳吏 美咲 你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们追着发光的东西走就掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去了 没事吧 受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小根 你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的 仁坂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的就是掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都下来了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.92,0:17:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要走到下面的登山路线的话就会有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.45,0:17:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该露出什么表情才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高崎同学在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是刚才发光的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都聚集到那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:46.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是萤火虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时期的应该是源氏萤火虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮 光芒在四处飞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些光 全都是虫子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.78,0:18:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是飞到脸上就太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.82,0:18:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 别说这种话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说可是生死问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.12,0:18:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小只的话没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是它在我身上产卵了怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 你把萤火虫当成什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.84,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怕虫子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我觉得萤火虫很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我还是第一次看到萤火虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我记得萤火虫只喝水的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且产卵之后立刻就会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.77,0:18:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个光芒 就是他们在拼命地恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们现在在进行着怎样的恋爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明消失之后不留点痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这些光芒们还是在拼命地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此刻恋爱着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友也好 喜欢的人也好 结婚对象也好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只要我们四人同看着这片景色
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我就是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两天一夜 眨眼就过去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:51.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 以后我们再一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走这边 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.14,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂你是坐地铁的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们一起走一段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈在这等会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 抱歉 拉着你来陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.78,0:20:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.28,0:20:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.70,0:20:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了昨天我看到萤火虫的时候也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个昨天你问我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然道歉可能没用 但是 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂 你是说我昨天问你有没有事瞒着我的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仁坂果然对高崎同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有叫做群马吉坟的古坟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,群马古坟 没有这种古坟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近读了一本以群马古坟为背景的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还有两层深沟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是群马那边的两层深沟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.05,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是太田天神山古坟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次带我一起去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 我们明天就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天要上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就后天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天也要上学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.57,0:21:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然就对古坟感兴趣了 我太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉奈 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道她是在担心我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 莉莉奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不明白 但是 不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我和莉莉奈的关系有些不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.06,0:22:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又是如此理所应当的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那时我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一件动摇我们之间关系的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:27.21,ED,,0,0,0,,さっきの言葉はまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:29.74,ED,,0,0,0,,I can't say I want to say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.82,ED,,0,0,0,,言えないままでしまってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:34.10,ED,,0,0,0,,I always lie
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:36.39,ED,,0,0,0,,星の瞬きほど早く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:38.82,ED,,0,0,0,,願い事するひまも無く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:40.96,ED,,0,0,0,,短い夏が終わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:43.78,ED,,0,0,0,,I can't say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:46.67,ED,,0,0,0,,Heart beat sound
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:52.67,ED,,0,0,0,,気づかないでいてね高鳴る鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:56.63,ED,,0,0,0,,Can't keep it to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.48,ED,,0,0,0,,自然にこぼれたはにかむ顔が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:05.81,ED,,0,0,0,,隠せないメッセージ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.81,0:23:07.64,ED,,0,0,0,,I know why I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:10.10,ED,,0,0,0,,未来を重ねた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:14.80,ED,,0,0,0,,二人の温もりが ここに残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.80,ED,,0,0,0,,ありふれた日々に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:19.40,ED,,0,0,0,,はじまりのキスを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:34.95,ED,,0,0,0,,ひとりの夜は 君の夢を見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:27.21,ED,,0,0,0,,刚才想说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.74,0:22:31.82,ED,,0,0,0,,还没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:36.39,ED,,0,0,0,,时间转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:38.82,ED,,0,0,0,,无暇许下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:40.96,ED,,0,0,0,,短暂夏日就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:52.67,ED,,0,0,0,,别让他发现 心声难以克制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.63,0:22:59.48,ED,,0,0,0,,自然流露的腼腆表情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:05.81,ED,,0,0,0,,掩藏不住心意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:10.10,ED,,0,0,0,,两人的温度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:14.80,ED,,0,0,0,,历经岁月 停留在此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:16.80,ED,,0,0,0,,在平淡的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:19.40,ED,,0,0,0,,时常回想起我们第一次的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:34.95,ED,,0,0,0,,孤独的夜里 在梦中与你相会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.27,0:23:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道料理的五十音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花椒 肉桂 木炭 猪油 还有...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.86,0:23:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天好蓝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 强迫恋爱的牢笼
